reviewText: Great inside tour of this historic instrument!  Very informative!

Even if you are only slightly interested in organs or music, this is a fascinating tour of one of the most complex machines ever built.  It's like touring the inside of a computer, only this one is mechanical.  True, more music would have been nice, but there are plenty of CD's available for that.  The editors had enough to do to fit this immense project onto one disc.
This DVD presents an excellent tour of the organ "innerds" but I wish it had more music actually being played on the organ.
